      <TermsOfUse><![CDATA[Boston College Acceptable Use Policy

The BC network is primarily for the use of members of the BC community to foster BC's mission.  Network access for guests of the University is provided as a courtesy, and should not be used to disrupt the BC network in any way.  If you choose to use the BC network below, you are subject to the policy found at www.bc.edu/techpolicy . You should be aware that (a) BC has the right to monitor your use of the network with automated systems that detect misuse of the BC network (e.g. spreading viruses, "hacking," copyright violations, or personally abusive behavior), and (b) your network access may be revoked at any time in the event that misuse is detected.
]]></TermsOfUse>
